POE-Filter-ErrorProof version 0.01
==================================

This module creates a wrapper around another POE::Filter to prevent it from die()ing or exit()ing the whole program.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules or libraries.

